snippet.title: Jump Dash Soar Official Steam Trailer
snippet.description: Jump Dash Soar is a frenetic, fast, and fun movement-based FPS. Build incredible speed with a powerful dash mechanic combined with rocket jumping, strafe running, slope jumps, and bounce pads! Coming soon to Steam!
